OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,FA victim of the says contracting
OL,7,FHepatitis C has been "a huge plight of
OL,8,Flife" after he was infected with
OL,9,Fcontaminated blood in 1986.
OL,11,FBill Wright, from Dumfries, was also
OL,12,Fsubsequently registered with
OL,13,Fhemophilia and now lives with liver
OL,14,Fcirrhosis.
OL,16,FHe has been one of the lead
OL,17,Fcampaigners calling for fair and
OL,18,Ffaster compensation for those affected
OL,19,Fby the scandal, and has also been the
OL,20,FChair of Hemophilia Scotland since it
OL,21,Fwas founded in 2012.
