OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,FHe said: "As the chairman of a
OL,7,Fcharity, I've sat in the front rooms
OL,8,Fof so many people who have been
OL,9,Faffected.
OL,11,F"Many many people have frankly lost
OL,12,Floved ones as a consequence of being
OL,13,Finfected with either hepatitis C or
OL,14,FHIV.
OL,16,F"Those stories are really brutal and
OL,17,Fthe impacts have been life changing."
