OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,FProtestors gathered on Abbington Green
OL,7,Foutside parliament on Wednesday to
OL,8,Frally MPs and put pressure on the
OL,9,Fgovernment to ensure victims of the
OL,10,Fscandal get the compensation they
OL,11,Fdeserve.
OL,13,F"We're looking to achieve two things
OL,14,Ftoday," Mr Wright said.
OL,16,F"The budget is of course taking place
OL,17,Fnext week, we want the government to
OL,18,Fmake sure that they allocate
OL,19,Fsufficient funds in order to pay
OL,20,Fcompensation to everyone who's been
OL,21,Faffected and infected by the disaster.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
