OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1709237245
OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,F"The second point is, we really need
OL,7,Fgovernment to be much more transparent
OL,8,Fin terms of what it's actually doing
OL,9,Fto make the arrangements to make those
OL,10,Fcompensation payments."
OL,12,FHe continued: "Until now, they've been
OL,13,Fpretty secretive, albeit they're
OL,14,Fclaiming that they're working very
OL,15,Fhard - we've seen no detail of that
OL,16,Fwhatsoever.
OL,18,F"So we're down here to try and get
OL,19,Fsome answers and to try and ensure
OL,20,Fthat sufficient funds are allocated."
