OL,6,FThe Infected Blood Inquiry made its
OL,7,Ffinal recommendations on compensation
OL,8,Ffor victims and their loved ones in
OL,9,FApril 2023.
OL,11,FAlmost a year since they were
OL,12,Fpublished calling for a compensation
OL,13,Fbody to be up and running by the end
OL,14,Fof 2023, campaigners say the
OL,15,Fgovernment continues to drag its heels
OL,16,Fover committing to compensation
OL,17,Fpayments.
