OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,F"In April last year, 10 months ago,
OL,7,FSir Brian Langstaff said arrangements
OL,8,Fshould start to be made now for
OL,9,Fcompensation," Mr Wright said.
OL,11,F"He set out a detailed report of how
OL,12,Fthat compensation should be paid -
OL,13,Fthat an arms length body should be
OL,14,Festablished
OL,16,F"There's no word whatsoever about that
OL,17,Fbody being established.
